articles.author: Christian Edwards, Catherine Nicholls
articles.title: Georgia rocked by fierce protests after government puts EU hopes on ice - CNN
articles.description: Georgia has been rocked by protests after its increasingly autocratic government said it would halt the former Soviet country’s bid to join the European Union.
